    <section class="fastpass-usage">
        <h2>How to Take Advantage of FastPass</h2>
        <p>Using FastPass is simple and can significantly enhance your experience with us. Here’s how you can make the most out of FastPass:</p>
        <ol>
            <li><strong>Plan Ahead:</strong> Review the attractions and services available with FastPass before your visit. Planning ahead helps you prioritize your activities.</li>
            <li><strong>Book Early:</strong> Obtain your FastPass as early as possible. Availability can be limited, and early booking ensures you get access to your preferred times and dates.</li>
            <li><strong>Use the FastPass Lane:</strong> When you arrive at an attraction with a FastPass, head straight to the FastPass lane. Show your pass to the attendant, and you’ll be able to skip the regular lines.</li>
            <li><strong>Enjoy Your Time:</strong> With less time spent waiting, you have more time to enjoy everything we have to offer. FastPass lets you maximize your fun and minimize downtime.</li>
        </ol>
        <p>By effectively using your FastPass, you can ensure a smoother, more enjoyable visit.</p>
